00:14:33.390 --> 00:14:34.560 align:middle line:90%
you're not dangerous.

00:14:34.560 --> 00:14:36.110 align:middle line:90%
I can.

00:14:36.110 --> 00:14:37.610 align:middle line:90%
>> Because I'm predictable.

00:14:37.610 --> 00:14:38.560 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:14:38.560 --> 00:14:42.910 align:middle line:84%
But if you have freedom and
can do something I don't know,

00:14:42.910 --> 00:14:50.130 align:middle line:84%
can't predict, then you're
