00:14:50.130 --> 00:14:51.570 align:middle line:84%
and I'm afraid of
you, you see, I

00:14:51.570 --> 00:14:54.250 align:middle line:84%
don't know what's
going to happen.

00:14:54.250 --> 00:14:55.780 align:middle line:90%
>> OK.

00:14:55.780 --> 00:14:59.275 align:middle line:84%
>> So that's what I meant by
the freedom is the flipside

00:14:59.275 --> 00:15:00.075 align:middle line:90%
of uncertainty.

