00:15:53.100 --> 00:15:55.150 align:middle line:84%
We don't need to bother
with it or something.

00:15:55.150 --> 00:15:56.280 align:middle line:90%
>> You mean, uncertainty?

00:15:56.280 --> 00:15:57.080 align:middle line:90%
>> Uncertainty.

00:15:57.080 --> 00:15:58.680 align:middle line:84%
The Heisenberg
Uncertainty Principle

00:15:58.680 --> 00:16:00.110 align:middle line:84%
has been kind of an
embarrassment to physicists.

00:16:00.110 --> 00:16:01.240 align:middle line:90%
>> One aspect of it.

00:16:01.240 --> 00:16:02.270 align:middle line:90%
>> Uh-huh.

00:16:02.270 --> 00:16:03.880 align:middle line:90%
>> The aspect, yes.

00:16:03.880 --> 00:16:06.400 align:middle line:84%
>> But uncertainty even like
the bugs in your helicopter.

00:16:06.400 --> 00:16:07.200 align:middle line:90%
>> Right.

00:16:07.200 --> 00:16:08.000 align:middle line:90%
>> Right.

00:16:08.000 --> 00:16:08.920 align:middle line:90%
Rather kind of.

00:16:08.920 --> 00:16:11.800 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, you don't want the
