00:16:14.330 --> 00:16:15.130 align:middle line:90%
>> Right.

00:16:15.130 --> 00:16:18.760 align:middle line:84%
>> You want to have the
uncertainty yourself,

00:16:18.760 --> 00:16:22.380 align:middle line:90%
