00:16:52.590 --> 00:16:54.980 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, also, this is
how you tap intuition.

00:16:54.980 --> 00:16:57.000 align:middle line:90%
>> Mm-hmm.

00:16:57.000 --> 00:16:59.800 align:middle line:84%
>> Remember there was a
story about somebody said

00:16:59.800 --> 00:17:04.060 align:middle line:84%
