that I worked with.

00:18:20.992 --> 00:18:22.200 align:middle line:90%
>> In other words, a psychic.

00:18:22.200 --> 00:18:22.760 align:middle line:90%
>> Psychic.

00:18:22.760 --> 00:18:23.560 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:18:23.560 --> 00:18:26.930 align:middle line:84%
>> And in fact, the most
impressive that I've known.

00:18:26.930 --> 00:18:28.290 align:middle line:90%
>> And you've known many.

