about avoiding.

00:19:21.930 --> 00:19:22.780 align:middle line:90%
>> Right.

00:19:22.780 --> 00:19:23.640 align:middle line:90%
>> Uh-huh.

00:19:23.640 --> 00:19:26.280 align:middle line:10%
>> So that's, something
will happen, I mean,

